:: Rainchark ::

:: Rainchark is startled by the message, but he understands the 
urgency of the task at hand and drops what he was doing.  Rainchark 
walks out of his room and turns on his jetpacks and flies out of the 
base, narrowly missing being destroyed as he screams through the 
hallways.  Once outside of the base, Rainchark heads towards 
Colorado. ::
